    <item>
      <title>迈克·柯林斯和德里克·杜利前往共和党佐治亚州参议院决选</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/05/19/us/politics/georgia-senate-primary.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[柯林斯和杜利将于 6 月 16 日面对面，争夺挑战受欢迎的民主党参议员乔恩·奥索夫的机会。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/05/19/us/politics/georgia-senate-primary.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 20 May 2026 03:19:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>得到民主党高层支持的工党领袖鲍勃·布鲁克斯赢得宾夕法尼亚州众议院初选</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/05/19/us/politics/bob-brooks-pennsylvania-house-primary.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[布鲁克斯先生将于秋季面对共和党众议员瑞安·麦肯齐(Ryan Mackenzie)。他赢得了全党的支持，包括佛蒙特州参议员伯尼·桑德斯和宾夕法尼亚州州长乔什·夏皮罗。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/05/19/us/politics/bob-brooks-pennsylvania-house-primary.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 20 May 2026 03:16:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>国税局放弃对特朗普及其家族的审计</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/05/19/us/politics/trump-irs-doj-lawsuit-audit.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[作为司法部赔偿基金协议的一部分，官员们发誓不会追究任何悬而未决的事项，包括涉及特朗普总统纳税申报表的事项。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/05/19/us/politics/trump-irs-doj-lawsuit-audit.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 20 May 2026 02:56:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>亚特兰大前市长赢得佐治亚州州长民主党初选</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/05/19/us/politics/bottoms-democrat-georgia-governor.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[凯莎·兰斯·博顿斯 (Keisha Lance Bottoms) 将成为民主党旗手，尽管人们对她担任该州最大城市市长的单一任期感到担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/05/19/us/politics/bottoms-democrat-georgia-governor.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 20 May 2026 02:31:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>早期战争的目标是让强硬派前总统担任伊朗领导人</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/05/19/us/politics/iran-israel-us-leader-ahmadinejad.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国官员表示，以色列发动袭击旨在将马哈茂德·艾哈迈迪·内贾德从德黑兰的软禁中解救出来，这是实现政权更迭并让他掌权的努力的一部分。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/05/19/us/politics/iran-israel-us-leader-ahmadinejad.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 19 May 2026 23:56:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>参议院投票采取措施迫使特朗普结束伊朗战争</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/05/19/us/politics/senate-iran-war-authorization.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在四名共和党支持者的支持下，民主党赢得了投票，提出一项决议，迫使总统结束敌对行动或赢得国会授权。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/05/19/us/politics/senate-iran-war-authorization.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 19 May 2026 23:00:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>由于通胀担忧加剧，债券收益率创 2007 年以来最高水平</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/05/19/business/bond-market-iran-war-inflation.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[自全球金融危机爆发以来，30年期美国国债收益率从未如此高。在欧洲和亚洲，收益率也有所上升。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/05/19/business/bond-market-iran-war-inflation.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 19 May 2026 22:17:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
